snippet.title: Death Kid - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
WISHLIST ON STEAM!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3456970/Death_Kid/

Death Kid is a fast-paced arena brawler where you must protect three souls trapped between life and death. Your goal is to give them enough time to open a passage leading deeper into the well, where lies the key to breaking the curse of immortality.
